CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 5, 1956, pg. 30 reads: "Ammon Fencing Team - "En garde" and "Touche" are trade words used by the fencing team organized at Ammon Center...Bottom photo shows Lavelle Russell and Eugene Wilson leaning the finer points from instructor Charles Edwell. - Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Ammon boys' fencing team, including Lavelle Russell and Eugene Wilson practicing with instructor Charles Edwell
